        Case 5:object.SetValue 0:FadingLevel(nr) = 1                   'ON
        Case 6, 7, 8:FadingLevel(nr) = FadingLevel(nr) + 1             'wait
        Case 9:object.SetValue 2:FadingLevel(nr) = FadingLevel(nr) + 1 'fading...
